+//! controllable pause/resume primitive on its clock. The rest of the
+//! tokio API is unchanged; see
+//! [`Builder::pausable_time`](crate::runtime::Builder::pausable_time)
+//! and the methods on [`Runtime`](crate::runtime::Runtime) (`pause`,
+//! `resume`, `wait_for_resume`, `run_unpausable`, etc.) for the
+//! pausable-specific bits, and the rest of these docs (inherited from
+//! upstream tokio) for everything else.
+//!
+//! ```toml
+//! [dependencies]
+//! tokio = { package = "pausable-tokio", version = "1.52.1", features = ["full"] }
+//! ```
